"\"<p data-start=\\\"226\\\" data-end=\\\"592\\\">In today\u2019s competitive market, sales leaders must do more than hit targets\u2014they must inspire trust, drive performance, and lead with purpose. This transformative workshop is designed to empower sales managers, team leads, and senior sales professionals with the mindset, skills, and tools needed to lead high-performing sales teams in a dynamic business environment.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"226\\\" data-end=\\\"592\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"594\\\" data-end=\\\"964\\\">Participants will explore how trust is the foundation of effective leadership\u2014both within the team and in client relationships\u2014and how it directly impacts sales outcomes. Through engaging discussions, real-world case studies, and hands-on activities, attendees will learn how to set clear goals, coach with impact, foster accountability, and deliver results that matter.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"594\\\" data-end=\\\"964\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"966\\\" data-end=\\\"1198\\\">Whether you're leading a small sales unit or managing regional teams, this session will help you lead with greater confidence, create a culture of performance, and achieve sustainable growth\u2014through trust-based leadership in action.<\/p>\""